{"tid":1053941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係覺得好孤單呀 無一個真心朋友又無女朋友","createTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T13:33:37.000Z","uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0a35350f8f6e9f660a64aa1f628762132ffb8e88","tid":1053941,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"Facebook 幾百個fds，無一個傾到心事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔嘅友誼好脆弱、虛偽。我完全唔夠膽講。<br />\n女仔fds想收兵咪會聽下囉，對你無興趣嘅都唔會當你係&rdquo;fd&rdquo;, 唔怪得d人話男女係無純友誼。<br />\n<br />\n女朋友又無個，有d想追你嘅人又感覺到唔係真心（似想呃你錢only）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日返工唔知為乜，喺香港份糧都改善唔到生活㗎啦，只係為生存。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好孤單呀𨳒，好撚想喊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cdfc615f4bb8a8a3824c411eb9c8eb0dce3644","tid":1053941,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11bab7eaf5b139f6acb8130e6113ddd6bdf25a6","tid":1053941,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"記得聽日都要準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a304f11a202b5104bc4a2a4a7678e14cf521a8ed","tid":1053941,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b11bab7eaf5b139f6acb8130e6113ddd6bdf25a6","tid":1053941,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"